Trong Oracle, c\'e2u l\f1\lang1066\u7879?nh IF-THEN-ELSE \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c s\u7917? d\u7909?ng \f2\'f0\f1\u7875? th\u7921?c thi m\f0\lang1033\'e3 khi m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t \f2\'f0i\f1\u7873?u ki\u7879?n l\f0\lang1033\'e0 TRUE ho\f1\lang1066\u7863?c th\u7921?c thi m\f0\lang1033\'e3 kh\'e1c n\f1\lang1066\u7871?u \f2\'f0i\f1\u7873?u ki\u7879?n cho gi\f0\lang1033\'e1 tr\f1\lang1066\u7883? FALSE.\f0\lang9\par
\b C\'fa ph\'e1p\b0\par
C\'f3 c\'e1c c\'fa ph\'e1p kh\'e1c nhau cho c\'e2u l\f1\lang1066\u7879?nh IF-THEN-ELSE.\par
\par
\b C\f0\lang1033\'fa ph\'e1p (IF-THEN)\b0\par
C\'fa ph\'e1p cho IF-THEN trong Oracle / PLSQL l\'e0:\par
\par
IF condition THEN\par
   \{...statements to execute when condition is TRUE...\}\par
END IF;\par
B\f1\lang1066\u7841?n s\u7917? d\u7909?ng c\f0\lang1033\'fa ph\'e1p IF-THEN, khi b\f1\lang1066\u7841?n ch\u7881? mu\u7889?n th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n c\f0\lang1033\'e1c c\'e2u l\f1\lang1066\u7879?nh khi \f2\'f0i\f1\u7873?u ki\u7879?n l\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'d0\f0\'daNG.\par
\par
\b C\'fa ph\'e1p (IF-THEN-ELSE)\b0\par
C\'fa ph\'e1p cho IF-THEN-ELSE trong Oracle / PLSQL l\'e0:\par
\par
IF condition THEN\par
   \{...statements to execute when condition is TRUE...\}\par
\par
ELSE\par
   \{...statements to execute when condition is FALSE...\}\par
\par
END IF;\par
B\f1\lang1066\u7841?n s\u7917? d\u7909?ng c\f0\lang1033\'fa ph\'e1p IF-THEN-ELSE, khi b\f1\lang1066\u7841?n mu\u7889?n th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n m\u7897?t nh\f0\lang1033\'f3m c\'e2u l\f1\lang1066\u7879?nh khi \f2\'f0i\f1\u7873?u ki\u7879?n l\f0\lang1033\'e0 TRUE ho\f1\lang1066\u7863?c m\u7897?t nh\f0\lang1033\'f3m c\'e2u l\f1\lang1066\u7879?nh kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c khi \f2\'f0i\f1\lang1066\u7873?u ki\u7879?n l\f0\lang1033\'e0 FALSE.\par
\par
\b C\'fa ph\'e1p (IF-THEN-ELSIF)\b0\par
C\'fa ph\'e1p cho IF-THEN-ELSIF trong Oracle / PLSQL l\'e0:\par
\par
IF condition1 THEN\par
   \{...statements to execute when condition1 is TRUE...\}\par
\par
ELSIF condition2 THEN\par
   \{...statements to execute when condition1 is FALSE and condition2 is TRUE...\}\par
\par
END IF;\par
B\f1\lang1066\u7841?n s\u7917? d\u7909?ng c\f0\lang1033\'fa ph\'e1p IF-THEN-ELSIF, khi b\f1\lang1066\u7841?n mu\u7889?n th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n m\u7897?t t\u7853?p h\u7907?p c\f0\lang1033\'e1c c\'e2u l\f1\lang1066\u7879?nh khi \f2\'f0i\f1\u7873?u ki\u7879?n 1 l\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'d0\f0\'daNG ho\f1\lang1066\u7863?c m\u7897?t t\u7853?p h\u7907?p c\f0\lang1033\'e1c c\'e2u l\f1\lang1066\u7879?nh kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c khi \f2\'f0i\f1\lang1066\u7873?u ki\u7879?n 2 l\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'d0\f0\'daNG.\par
\par
\b C\'fa ph\'e1p (IF-THEN-ELSIF-ELSE)\b0\par
C\'fa ph\'e1p cho IF-THEN-ELSIF-ELSE trong Oracle / PLSQL l\'e0:\par
\par
IF condition1 THEN\par
   \{...statements to execute when condition1 is TRUE...\}\par
\par
ELSIF condition2 THEN\par
   \{...statements to execute when condition1 is FALSE and condition2 is TRUE...\}\par
\par
ELSE\par
   \{...statements to execute when both condition1 and condition2 are FALSE...\}\par
\par
END IF;\par
B\f1\lang1066\u7841?n s\u7917? d\u7909?ng c\f0\lang1033\'fa ph\'e1p IF-THEN-ELSIF-ELSE, khi b\f1\lang1066\u7841?n mu\u7889?n th\u7921?c hi\u7879?n m\u7897?t t\u7853?p h\u7907?p c\f0\lang1033\'e1c c\'e2u l\f1\lang1066\u7879?nh khi \f2\'f0i\f1\u7873?u ki\u7879?n 1 l\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'d0\f0\'daNG, m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t t\u7853?p h\u7907?p c\f0\lang1033\'e1c c\'e2u l\f1\lang1066\u7879?nh kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c khi \f2\'f0i\f1\lang1066\u7873?u ki\u7879?n 2 l\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'d0\f0\'daNG ho\f1\lang1066\u7863?c m\u7897?t t\u7853?p h\u7907?p c\f0\lang1033\'e1c c\'e2u l\f1\lang1066\u7879?nh kh\f0\lang1033\'e1c khi t\f1\lang1066\u7845?t c\u7843? c\f0\lang1033\'e1c \f2\'f0i\f1\lang1066\u7873?u ki\u7879?n tr\f2\u432?\f1\u7899?c \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'f3 (v\'ed d\f1\lang1066\u7909?: \f2\'f0i\f1\u7873?u ki\u7879?n1 v\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'f0i\f1\lang1066\u7873?u ki\u7879?n 2 ) l\f0\lang1033\'e0 FALSE.\par
\par
\b Ghi ch\'fa\b0\par
Khi m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t \f2\'f0i\f1\u7873?u ki\u7879?n \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c t\f0\lang1033\'ecm th\f1\lang1066\u7845?y l\f0\lang1033\'e0 TRUE, c\'e2u l\f1\lang1066\u7879?nh IF-THEN-ELSE s\u7869? th\u7921?c thi m\f0\lang1033\'e3 t\f2\u432?\u417?ng \f1\lang1066\u7913?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0 kh\'f4ng \f2\'f0\f0\'e1nh gi\'e1 c\'e1c \f2\'f0i\f1\lang1066\u7873?u ki\u7879?n n\u7919?a.\par
N\u7871?u kh\f0\lang1033\'f4ng c\'f3 \f2\'f0i\f1\lang1066\u7873?u ki\u7879?n n\f0\lang1033\'e0o \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7907?c \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e1p \f1\lang1066\u7913?ng, ph\u7847?n ELSE c\u7911?a c\f0\lang1033\'e2u l\f1\lang1066\u7879?nh IF-THEN-ELSE s\u7869? \f2\'f0\u432?\f1\u7907?c th\u7921?c thi.\par
\f2\'d0i\f1\u7873?u quan tr\u7885?ng c\u7847?n l\f2\u432?u \f0\lang1033\'fd l\'e0 c\'e1c ph\f1\lang1066\u7847?n ELSIF v\f0\lang1033\'e0 ELSE l\'e0 t\'f9y ch\f1\lang1066\u7885?n.\par
\b Th\f0\lang1033\'ed d\f1\lang1066\u7909?\b0\par
Sau \f2\'f0\f0\lang1033\'e2y l\'e0 v\'ed d\f1\lang1066\u7909? s\u7917? d\u7909?ng c\f0\lang1033\'e2u l\f1\lang1066\u7879?nh IF-THEN-ELSE trong m\u7897?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0m Oracle:\par
\par
\b\i CREATE OR REPLACE Function IncomeLevel\par
   ( name_in IN varchar2 )\par
   RETURN varchar2\par
IS\par
   monthly_value number(6);\par
   ILevel varchar2(20);\par
   cursor c1 is\par
     SELECT monthly_income\par
     FROM employees\par
     WHERE name = name_in;\par
BEGIN\par
   open c1;\par
   fetch c1 into monthly_value;\par
   close c1;\par
   IF monthly_value <= 4000 THEN\par
      ILevel := 'Low Income';\par
   ELSIF monthly_value > 4000 and monthly_value <= 7000 THEN\par
      ILevel := 'Avg Income';\par
   ELSIF monthly_value > 7000 and monthly_value <= 15000 THEN\par
      ILevel := 'Moderate Income';\par
   ELSE\par
      ILevel := 'High Income';\par
   END IF;\par
   RETURN ILevel;\par
END;\par
\b0\i0 Trong v\'ed d\f1\lang1066\u7909? v\u7873? c\f0\lang1033\'e2u l\f1\lang1066\u7879?nh IF-THEN-ELSE n\f0\lang1033\'e0y, ch\'fang t\'f4i \f2\'f0\f0\'e3 t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o m\u7897?t h\f0\lang1033\'e0m c\'f3 t\'ean l\'e0 IncomeLevel. N\'f3 c\'f3 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t tham s\u7889? g\u7885?i l\f0\lang1033\'e0 name_in v\'e0 n\'f3 tr\f1\lang1066\u7843? v\u7873? m\u7897?t varchar2. H\f0\lang1033\'e0m s\f1\lang1066\u7869? tr\u7843? v\u7873? m\u7913?c thu nh\u7853?p d\u7921?a tr\f0\lang1033\'ean t\'ean c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a nh\f0\lang1033\'e2n vi\'ean.\par
